CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 19, 1945 Page 13 reads: "Poster Contest winners-- Winners in the high school competition sponsored by the Pittsburgh Branch of Federal Union, Inc, pose with their entries at Carnegie Museum. Left to right: Joseph Schumacher, junior at Connelly Vocational School; John Wall, senior at Peabody High; Roland Lucas, senior at Peabody High; Roland Lucas, Senior at South Hills High." -- Harris Photo.
TitMainTitle: Joseph Schumacher, John Wall, and Roland Lucas, holding winning posters of high school competition sponsored by Pittsburgh Branch of Federal Union Inc. standing in interior with showcases
